name: multiple_views fellatio from_side pov concept
description:
Multiple views, with from side on the top, and pov on the majority.

Trained on hiiro_h, who has a lot of bar_censors, and exclusively does dark skinned males.

I tried training out the dark-skinned male and bar_censors, to let you choose if you want it, but that didn't take.

Combines well with https://civitai.com/models/11830/steampunkengibarcensor-bar-censorship for getting rid of the bar censor.

But the overall, effect of having from side, and pov worked out pretty well, but note, since all of the source was from hiiro_h for that, their style is dominant.

modelVersions.description: first version, the style is stronger than I'd like, and the the bar_censors and dark-skinned male seemed burnt in, so I'll probably run my data set through img2img and retrain on that when I have the time.
